      "turn_id": 1,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "我们需要画一个云原生部署流程图，核心是几个关键组件：Docker镜像、Helm Chart、Serverless和服务网格。我想用简洁的节点名，比如用Audit代表Docker镜像，Bail代表Helm Chart。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Audit",
        "Bail",
        "Code",
        "Define",
        "CloudNative_DockerImage",
        "CloudNative_HelmChart",
        "CloudNative_Serverless",
        "CloudNative_ServiceMesh"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 2,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "明白了，Audit和Bail都映射到Docker镜像吗？还是Audit是Docker镜像，Bail是Helm Chart？另外Code和Define分别对应Serverless和服务网格对吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Audit",
        "Bail",
        "Code",
        "Define"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "对，Audit是Docker镜像，Bail是Helm Chart。但等等，我补充一个Barg节点，它也代表Docker镜像，和Audit有区别——Audit是官方镜像，Barg是业务自定义镜像。Code是Serverless，Define是服务网格。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Audit",
        "Bail",
        "Barg",
        "Code",
        "Define"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "好的，已创建五个主节点：Audit（Docker镜像）、Bail（Helm Chart）、Barg（自定义Docker镜像）、Code（Serverless）、Define（服务网格）。接下来画关系线？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Audit",
        "Bail",
        "Barg",
        "Code",
        "Define"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 5,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "关系是这样的：Code指向Define，表示Serverless调用服务网格；Define指向Barg，服务网格需要加载业务镜像；Audit也指向Define，官方镜像同样注册到网格。Bail和Barg要双向连接，Helm Chart管理镜像部署。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Code",
        "Define",
        "Barg",
        "Audit",
        "Bail"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 6,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "已添加：Code→Define、Define→Barg、Audit→Define、Bail↔Barg的双向关系。还有别的流向吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Code",
        "Define",
        "Barg",
        "Audit",
        "Bail"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 7,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "还需要三个上游节点：Place、Signal、Risk。Place触发Press动作到某个节点，Signal指向Barg，Risk指向Signal形成链式依赖。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Place",
        "Press",
        "Signal",
        "Risk",
        "Barg"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 8,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "Press是动作标签不是节点对吧？Place→Press指向哪里？还有Risk→Signal→Barg这条链，Risk和Signal本身是什么类型的节点？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Place",
        "Press",
        "Risk",
        "Signal",
        "Barg"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 9,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "Press是动作标签，Place—Press这个关系我画错了，应该是Place指向Press？不对，重新说：Place到Press是一条带标签的边，但Press不是独立节点。实际上按Mermaid语法，Place -- Press 表示Place到某个目标，Press是文本标签。让我想想...目标应该是Bail，表示Place触发Press动作来部署Helm Chart。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Place",
        "Press",
        "Bail"
      ],
      "is_repair": true
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 10,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "repair",
      "utterance": "收到，修正为Place到Bail的边，标签是Press。那Risk和Signal呢？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Place",
        "Press",
        "Bail",
        "Risk",
        "Signal"
      ],
      "is_repair": true
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 11,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "Risk→Signal→Barg，Risk是风险评估节点，Signal是信号检测，风险触发检测，检测完成后拉取Barg镜像。",
      "elements_involved": [
